---
title: Balsamic Sirloin Steak with velvety mash and baby spinach
description: The already delicious Irish sirloin steak in this recipe is elevated to new heights with the addition of a rich and buttery balsamic glaze. Creamy mash and tender carrots pull the whole recipe together for a meal that's simple, elegant, and endlessly appetising.
